## Backend API Endpoints

### 1. Get Journey History (Paginated)
```
GET /api/mobile/driver/journeys? vehicleId={id}&page={page}&limit={limit}&startDate={date}&endDate={date}
Authorization: Bearer {token}

Query Parameters:
- vehicleId: string (required)
- page: number (default: 1)
- limit: number (default: 20)
- startDate: ISO date string (optional)
- endDate: ISO date string (optional)
- search: string (optional - search destination)

Response:
